---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ScienceBacked from '../components/ScienceBacked.astro';
import LeadForm from '../components/LeadForm.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="There Is Hope — PornLies"
  description="No matter where you are, there is hope. Real freedom from pornography is possible."
  currentPage="/hope"
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hope-hero">
    <div class="container hope-hero__inner">

      <!-- Dove: FA Pro light (outline) dove via kit, fallback SVG -->
      <div class="hope-hero__dove" aria-hidden="true">
        <i class="fa-thin fa-dove"></i>
      </div>

      <h1 class="hope-hero__title animate-fadeup">
        There is <span class="text-tan">hope.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hope-hero__subtitle animate-fadeup animate-fadeup--delay-1">
        <em>No matter where you are, there is hope!</em>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Body copy -->
  <section class="section hope-body-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hope-body">

        <p>Whether you're stuck and desperate to break free or you love someone struggling,
          <strong>there is hope for you.</strong></p>

        <p>You might feel worn down, tired, and hopeless because porn's lie that "there is no way
          out." You might feel like you are too far gone because you've tried so many times to end
          your relationship with porn without success. Or, perhaps you love someone stuck in an
          endless cycle of indulgence and regret.</p>

        <p>We are here to tell you that <strong>there is hope and that freedom is just around the
          bend</strong> — one step at a time. Your future depends on your choices right now. You
          can be defeated, or you can rise. If you feel like you are at rock bottom — that's great;
          the only way from here is UP!</p>

        <p>We know it's not easy to stop on your own because you would have already done it if it
          was. We know that shame can be so debilitating it keeps us from seeking help because we
          don't want anyone to know. But we also know that people want to be seen and loved for who
          they are at their core. When we live in shame, we lose sight of our authentic selves.</p>

        <p>We know what the struggle and the cycle is like because <strong>many of us have been
          there too!</strong> You are not alone; we can promise you that. Nothing you have done or
          are struggling with will make us judge you. Porn is a liar, and you have been duped by
          its powerful, manipulative, deceptive lies.</p>

        <!-- Guide download -->
        <div class="hope-guide">
          <p class="hope-guide__label">Download the guide:</p>
          <a href="#hope-download" class="btn btn--red hope-guide__btn">
            5 Things You Can Do Today to Kick Porn to the Curb
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Science + testimonials -->
  <ScienceBacked />

  <!-- Single download form — no duplicate newsletter -->
  <section class="section" id="hope-download" aria-labelledby="hope-guide-heading">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="cta-block__eyebrow">Download the Guide:</p>
        <h2 class="cta-block__title" id="hope-guide-heading">
          Ways to Kick Porn to the Curb Today
        </h2>
        <LeadForm id="hope-guide-form" submitLabel="Get the Free Guide" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ── Hero ── */
  .hope-hero {
    padding-top: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    padding-bottom: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .hope-hero__inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
  }
  .hope-hero__dove {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    color: #c4a882;
    opacity: 0.85;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .hope-hero__title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #F5EDD7;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
  }
  .hope-hero__subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Body ── */
  .hope-body-section { padding-top: 1.5rem; }
  .hope-body {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }
  .hope-body p {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.1rem);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #F5EDD7;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .hope-body strong { color: #F5EDD7; font-weight: 700; }

  /* ── Guide CTA ── */
  .hope-guide {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .hope-guide__label, .hope-body p.hope-guide__label {
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);  /* unified with guide-label */
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #F5EDD7;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .hope-guide__btn {
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
    max-width: 520px;
    width: 100%;
    white-space: normal;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  /* ── Form section ── */
  .form-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #FFBE00;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .form-title {
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #F5EDD7;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
</style>
